'''Setswana''' ke puo ee buiwang mo mafatsheng a [[Aforika Borwa]], [[Botswana]], [[Namibia]] le [[Zimbabwe]]. Ke nngwe ya dipuo tsa semmuso kwa [[Aforika Borwa]] fa kwa [[Botswana]] gone e le puo ee tsewang e le yone ya lefatshe ka bophara. Banni bangwe ba Botswana ba tsalwa ba sa bue Setswana jaaka [[Bakgalagadi]], [[Bakalaka]] le ba bangwe. Ba se ithuta mo mebileng le ko sekolong. 

Setswana se sikana thata le Sesotho, puo e e buiwang ko Aforika Borwa le Lesotho. Se se dira gore babui ba dipuo tse ba tlhaloganyane botlhofo go gaisa ba dipuo tse dingwe tse di mabapi.

Bontsi jwa batho ba ba buang Setswana ba fitlhelwa kwa lefatsheng la [[Aforika Borwa]] bogolo segolo mo diporofenseng tsa [[Bokone Bophirima]] (North West) le [[Kapa Bokone]]. [[Batswana]] ba [[Aforika Borwa]] ba ka nna didikadike di le 3.4 fa [[Batswana]] ba Botswana ba ka nna sedikadike le go feta (gongwe 1.3). [[Batswana]] ba [[Namibia]] le Ba Zimbabwe ba palo potlana. Legale ditirelo tsa kgaso tsa [[Namibia]] di gasa gape ka Setswana.

Setswana ke puo ee monatenate, ee nonneng ka e bile e buiwa mo mafatsheng a mane a a mo borwa jwa [[Aforika]]. Baithuti bangwe ba dipuo ba re Setswana ke nngwe ya dipuo tse di matswakabele thata go gaisa tse dingwe tsa borwa jwa [[Aforika]]. 

Setswana se na le manatetsha puo a mantsi jaaka [[diane]], [[dithamalakwane]] le [[maele]].

